Nigerian businessman, Obinna Iyiegbu, popularly known as Obi Cubana, has stated that getting married to his wife is one of his life’s best decisions. On his Instagram page on Tuesday, the popular club owner noted that he performed the traditional marriage rites on his wife, Ebele, exactly 14 years ago. He shared a video of himself and his wife on his page and showered her with praises. The businessman wrote, “The traditional wine carrying of this beautiful model-queen took place exactly 14 years ago this day, in Obosi, Idemmili North LGA of Anambra State! “This is one of my life’s best decisions; getting married to this damsel! Ok, next week Tuesday 14th is our 14th wedding anniversary. The story continues then!” Showering her with praises in his dialect, Obi Cubana wrote, “Nwanyi oma, mkpuru mma m, tomato jos m, udala usö m, azu cubana m, the sweetest thing that can NEVER cause me diabetes! I celebrate you everyday biko!” Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com